# Per-project coord worker configuration.
#
# Copy to `<your-project>/.coord/config.env` and set any keys you need.
# Parsed line-by-line as `KEY=value` by the worker (not shell-sourced — no shell expansion or quoting). Everything here is
# OPTIONAL — built-in defaults apply when a key is unset.

# Model passed to `claude --model` for the Claude coder/reviewer in this project.
# CLAUDE_MODEL=claude-sonnet-5

# Model passed to `claude --model` for the watchdog that diagnoses stuck tasks.
# COORD_WATCHDOG_MODEL=claude-sonnet-5

# See docs/coordination.md and docs/claude-coordination.md for the full set.
